{"tid":2019931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警藏毒一事，顯示警隊人士跟納粹德軍無異","createTime":"2020-05-16T15:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T12:24:55.000Z","uid":98542,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9084101799f5cd1a5cd2453d1fefd34933781346","tid":2019931,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:42:34.000Z","msg":"小弟早排睇Netflix套二戰大事記<br />\n第一集就講到二戰初期既「閃電戰」(blitzkrieg)<br />\n去到節目中段就提及到當時納粹德國點樣加快行動速度<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當中提及到Pervitin係當時德軍前線士兵常用既提神藥物<br />\n而Pervitin就係依家我哋所稱既<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">安非他命/冰毒</span></strong></span></span><br />\n由於當時對藥物副作用既認識唔多<br />\n所以Pervitin被當時德軍廣泛使用<br />\n亦都成為咗「閃電戰」既成功因素之一<br />\n<br />\n我對安非他命既藥物副作用做咗少少research<br />\n當中包括：<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>dysphoria（煩躁）, self-confidence（自信感）, irritability（容易受刺激）, grandiosity (優越感）, fixation（固執）, hyperactivity（過度活躍）, hallucinations （幻覺）, violent behavior（暴力行為）</ins></span><br />\n係咪好熟面口呢？<br />\n因為班黑警全部都有呢啲行為<br />\n亦都可以解釋到點解佢哋可以咁撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要記住<br />\n啲毒品係邊度起出嚟架？元朗。<br />\n警務處處長姓咩架？姓鄧。<br />\n元朗係圍村既人姓咩架？姓鄧。<br />\n反黑組阿頭係邊個呀？李桂華。<br />\n佢出席過咩飯局呀？[url]【武漢肺炎警察Happy】PPRB江永祥郭嘉銓黃埔「榴槤宴客」 14K殯儀猛人同場&nbsp;|&nbsp;2020-02-09&nbsp;|&nbsp;壹週刊&nbsp;|&nbsp;蘋果日報<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_724240_0&amp;i=20200209［/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_724240_0%26i%3D20200209%EF%BC%BB%2Furl%5D&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=3acbab1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_724240_0%26i%3D20200209%EF%BC%BB%2Furl%5D&h=9b54b08d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_724240_0&amp;i=20200209［/url]</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於真相係點，大家心照喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係講述納粹德軍係戰爭入面使用藥物既報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/09/books/high-on-hitler-and-meth-book-says-nazis-were-fueled-by-drugs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2016%2F12%2F09%2Fbooks%2Fhigh-on-hitler-and-meth-book-says-nazis-were-fueled-by-drugs.html&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=e87156bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/09/books/high-on-hitler-and-meth-book-says-nazis-were-fueled-by-drugs.html</a>"},{"pid":"767aebf5db61ec70e710deb150382abaf28c8333","tid":2019931,"uid":56205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"班畜生唔駛伏冰都躁狂架啦"},{"pid":"dff67a68bd98734801a0b04f6dae8848a7ea57e4","tid":2019931,"uid":98542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:52:02.000Z","msg":"我明白呢篇野對現時局勢冇咩幫助<br />\n小弟除咗枝筆之外<br />\n基本上真係乜撚用都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家如果可以的話<br />\n幫下小弟推一推po<br />\n嚟緊可能會為呢單野寫個英文版<br />\n大家推一推，當畀少少支持小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三萬，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7695a5d00e3ce8673cb918d072e7a5c67c725d6b","tid":2019931,"uid":140538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T15:56:27.000Z","msg":"可以結合影像分析下佢哋行動時吸邊種<br />\n我覺得有唔同種類"},{"pid":"ca9a0cc3bc393995c46bc0c39156aa8f9ea60bfa","tid":2019931,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi